        <span>What about the tyrolean traverse?</span>
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">A cable crosses a gorge that you clip into with a harness (provided). It's exciting but safe if you follow instructions. Not technical but can be intimidating.</div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="faq-item">
      <div class="faq-question" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
        <span>Can I do it without camping experience?</span>
        <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-answer">No. You need solid backcountry camping skills including in severe weather. This is not a trek to learn on.</div>
    </div>
  
    <div class="faq-item">
